## DATA MAPPING SUMMARY TABLE

| KPI # | KPI Name | Primary Table(s) | Key Fields | Update Frequency |
|-------|----------|------------------|------------|------------------|
| 1-45 | Financial KPIs | transactions, budget_line_items, budgets | total_amount, actual_amount | Real-time to Daily |
| 46-90 | Ticket & Attendance | tickets, ticket_tiers, check_ins, events | ticket_status, final_price, checked_in_at | Real-time to Daily |
| 91-145 | Operational Efficiency | tasks, project_milestones, staff_assignments, vendors, vendor_deliverables | task_status, due_date, completed_at | Daily |
| 146-175 | Marketing & Engagement | marketing_campaigns, email_campaigns, social_media_posts, brand_mentions | engagement metrics, campaign_stats | Hourly to Daily |
| 176-200 | Customer Experience | survey_responses, communications, incidents | rating fields, resolution times | After event |

---

## IMPLEMENTATION NOTES

### Critical Data Dependencies
1. **Transactions Table**: Foundation for ALL financial KPIs (1-45)
2. **Tickets Table**: Foundation for ALL attendance KPIs (46-90)
3. **Tasks Table**: Foundation for operational KPIs (91-110)
4. **Survey Responses**: Foundation for satisfaction KPIs (176-200)

### Required Integrations
- Payment processors (Stripe, Square) → transactions
- Ticketing platforms → tickets, check_ins
- Email marketing (Mailchimp, SendGrid) → email_campaigns
- Social media APIs → social_media_posts, brand_mentions
- Web analytics (Google Analytics) → conversion tracking
- Survey tools → survey_responses

### Calculation Triggers
- **Real-time**: Transactions, check-ins, ticket sales
- **Hourly**: Marketing campaigns, web analytics
- **Daily**: Budget variance, task completion, vendor performance
- **Weekly**: Staff metrics, vendor relationships
- **After Event**: Survey-based KPIs, final reconciliation

